  "message": "feat(benchmark): Model2Vec static embedder benchmark results\n\nDownloaded and benchmarked Model2Vec static embedders:\n\n| Model                    | Latency p50 | Throughput    |\n|--------------------------|-------------|---------------|\n| hash-fnv1a-384 (baseline)| 0.074ms     | 398,850/s     |\n| potion-multilingual-128M | 0.574ms     | 52,144/s      |\n| potion-retrieval-32M     | 0.91ms      | 33,512/s      |\n| all-MiniLM-L6-v2         | 128ms       | 228/s         |\n| bge-small-en-v1.5        | 230ms       | 120/s         |\n\nKey finding: Model2Vec embedders are 140-224x faster than\ntransformers while providing real semantic embeddings.\n\nPart of bd-1g6: Static Embedding Model Evaluation\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
